  <thing id="cEsfSilvEx" name="Silver Exorcism" description="At 5th level and higher, an exorcist of the Silver Flame gains a +2 bonus on Charisma checks to force possessing spirits out of the bodies they inhabit, as well as on all dispel checks and caster level checks to harm, banish, or overcome the spell resistance of evil outsiders. This includes dispel checks to dispel a {i}summon monster{/i} spell when the summoned monster is an evil outsider. However, the bodies they inhabit take 1d6 points of sacred damage." compset="ClSpecial">
